##### Google Talk

Google has launched is own Jabber service know as Google Talk. If you have a Gmail account, it’s probably easier to use Google Talk. You can choose to use the official Google Talk client (Windows only) or any other client such as Gaim, iChat or Psi.

=> http://www.google.com/talk/ Google Talk
=> http://www.google.com/talk/start.html official Google Talk client
=> http://www.google.com/support/talk/bin/answer.py?answer=24073 Gaim
=> http://www.google.com/support/talk/bin/answer.py?answer=24076 iChat
=> http://www.google.com/support/talk/bin/answer.py?answer=24074 Psi

If you don’t have a GMail account and want one, just send me your email adress and put « GMail request » in the title.

=> /contact send me

Once you have your GMail account, you can talk with every other Jabber or Google Talk users. No matter that one of your contact is using fritalk.com and the other im.apinc.org, just enjoy !

